    "description": "Solvvy Inc. provides warranty services and software as a service (SaaS) products. The Company offers warranty, inspection, and maintenance services, comprising home appliance warranty, long-term building guarantee, earthquake guarantee, ground compensation, warranty for used homes, maintenance fund accumulation service, home manager and bot, repair, and contact center services; system development consulting services; and SaaS products, such as home manager, home BOT, Genba assist, KROX, my class, and other products. It also develops products and services in the renewable energy and education ICT fields. In addition, it offers factoring services, escrow services, and a valuation service. The company was formerly known as Japan Living Warranty Inc and changed its name to Solvvy Inc. in November 2024. The company was incorporated in 2009 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan."
